like Tulotero, they end up becoming

00:00:45.160 --> 00:00:46.100
customers, they put

00:00:46.100 --> 00:00:47.840
their data on the credit

00:00:47.840 --> 00:00:48.900
card, and they end up

00:00:48.900 --> 00:00:49.720
being players, and

00:00:49.720 --> 00:00:51.880
the more recurrent it is better.

