The metric is the one you already

00:05:31.980 --> 00:05:33.640
know, the most common.

00:05:33.640 --> 00:05:35.080
In this case it would be the ARP.

00:05:35.080 --> 00:05:36.260
We should constantly measure

00:05:36.260 --> 00:05:39.380
the average expenditure

00:05:39.380 --> 00:05:41.360
of customers in a year.

00:05:42.240 --> 00:05:43.760
If you do things well, it should

