if we are on the right track and

00:06:06.340 --> 00:06:07.700
we are finding the most suitable

00:06:07.700 --> 00:06:09.140
channels.

00:06:09.360 --> 00:06:10.940
Well, because here metrics are

00:06:10.940 --> 00:06:12.820
usually very common and is, for example,

00:06:12.820 --> 00:06:14.220
the cost per lead.

