important to also keep in mind that

00:06:31.680 --> 00:06:34.200
not only you have to measure how much

00:06:34.200 --> 00:06:35.460
it costs you to bring a customer,

00:06:35.460 --> 00:06:36.640
but if you are testing different

00:06:36.640 --> 00:06:38.780
channels, it is interesting to

00:06:38.780 --> 00:06:40.740
keep in mind that you can be capturing

00:06:40.740 --> 00:06:42.640
users of different profile that

00:06:42.640 --> 00:06:45.200
at the end of some are more

00:06:45.200 --> 00:06:46.580
profitable than others.

