00:07:17.200 --> 00:07:20.520
experiments by comparing two hypotheses

00:07:20.520 --> 00:07:24.220
and seeing whether one of the two,

00:07:24.220 --> 00:07:25.560
A or B, has a positive or

00:07:25.560 --> 00:07:27.340
better impact on these metrics

00:07:27.340 --> 00:07:29.060
that we have identified as important.

